Verified: 2026-05-23
}

\subsection{Automated Trading Usage}{
\itemize{
\item \strong{Stale Order Cleanup}: Cancel orders that have not filled within a timeout window.
\item \strong{Position Exit}: Cancel pending limit orders before placing a market close to avoid double fills.
}
}

