\subsection{\code{KucoinFuturesTrading$cancel_order_by_client_oid()}}{
  Cancel Order by Client Order ID

Cancels an open futures order using the client-provided order ID. Requires
the symbol to disambiguate in case client OIDs are reused across symbols.
\subsection{Workflow}{
\enumerate{
\item \strong{Request}: Authenticated DELETE with the client OID in the URL path and \code{symbol} as a query parameter.
\item \strong{Parsing}: Returns \code{data.table} with the cancelled client order ID.
}
}

\subsection{API Endpoint}{

