\subsection{\code{KucoinFuturesTrading$get_order_by_client_oid()}}{
  Get Order by Client Order ID

Retrieves full details of a single futures order by its client-provided
order ID. Useful when the system order ID was not stored at placement time.
\subsection{Workflow}{
\enumerate{
\item \strong{Request}: Authenticated GET with \code{clientOid} as a query parameter.
\item \strong{Parsing}: Returns a single-row \code{data.table} with all order fields.
\item \strong{Timestamp Conversion}: Coerces \code{created_at} and \code{updated_at} from milliseconds to POSIXct.
}
}

\subsection{API Endpoint}{

